iv><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">b[@ 2] = 7;//此时改变的是新的数组</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(a[2]);//5</div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(b[2]);//7</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">//-------------------------------------------------</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">a[1] = 1;</div><div class=\"line\">a[2] = 2;</div><div class=\"line\">a[3] = 3;</div><div class=\"line\">a[4] = 4;</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">b = a; //获取a的所有数据</div><div class=\"line\">b[5] = 2;// 移动一位，并创建新的数组</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">b[@ 2] = 5;//此时不会再改变数组a的值</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(a[2]);//2</div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(b[2]);//5</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">a[2] = 4; //一维数组</div><div class=\"line\">a[0,1] = 5;//二维数组</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(array_length_2d(a,0));//3(0,1,2)</div><div class=\"line\">show_debug_message(a[0,2]);//4</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"数组的accessors。12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031323334353637var a,b,c;a[2] = 4;show_debug_message(a[2]);//4b = a;b[@ 2] = ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":7,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"GMS教程","slug":"GMS教程","count":3,"path":"api/tags/GMS教程.json"}]},{"title":"GMS优先度引擎、状态管理等发布","slug":"game/Priority-Engine","date":"2015-08-10T16:26:24.000Z","updated":"2017-05-12T06:23:40.670Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/game/Priority-Engine.json","excerpt":"<p>当当当，发布一个GMS的优先度引擎。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优先度引擎\"><a href=\"#优先度引擎\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优先度引擎\"></a>优先度引擎</h3><p>下载请点击：<a href=\"https://marketplace.yoyogames.com/assets/2194/priorityengine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">yoyo市场链接</a><br>查看源码：<a href=\"https://coding.net/u/deciia/p/OpenGmsLibs/git\" target=\"_blank\" rel